(window.webpackJsonp=window.webpackJsonp||[]).push([[87],{670:function(e){e.exports={name:"textbox",displayName:"TextBox *文本框*",group:"form",text:'\n用于输入一些简短的文本内容；\n\n``` demo.87d726e5\nimport { TextBox } from \'nami\'\n\nrender(<TextBox placeholder="Please enter some text ..." />)\n```\n\n## 状态\n\n通过 `state` 参数定义文本框状态：\n\n``` demo.070e4e3b\nimport { TextBox } from \'nami\'\n\nrender(\n    <div>\n        <TextBox state="success" defaultValue="success" />\n        <TextBox state="warning" defaultValue="warning" />\n        <TextBox state="danger" defaultValue="danger" />\n    </div>\n)\n```\n\n## 禁用、只读\n\n通过 `disabled` 或 `readOnly` 参数，可以设置文本框为禁用或只读状态：\n\n``` demo.c48c74dd\nimport { TextBox } from \'nami\'\n\nrender(\n    <div>\n        <TextBox disabled defaultValue="disabled" />\n        <TextBox readOnly defaultValue="readonly" />\n    </div>\n)\n```\n\n**注意：**禁用输入框没有状态样式：\n\n``` demo.890555d8\nimport { TextBox } from \'nami\'\n\nrender(\n    <div>\n        <TextBox disabled state="success" defaultValue="disabled - success" />\n        <TextBox readOnly state="success" defaultValue="readonly - success" />\n    </div>\n)\n```\n\n## 参数\n\n### TextBox\n\n| 参数           | 说明             | 类型                                             | 默认值  |\n| -------------- | ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------ | ------- |\n| `value`        | 表单值           | `string`                                         |         |\n| `defaultValue` | 默认表单值       | `string`                                         |         |\n| `type`         | 内容类型         | `string`                                         | `text`  |\n| `state`        | 状态             | `\'success\'` &#124; `\'warning\'` &#124; `\'danger\'` |         |\n| `disabled`     | 是否禁用         | `boolean`                                        | `false` |\n| `onChange`     | 选中状态改变事件 | `(event: ChangeEvent, value: string) => void`    |         |\n',path:"./src/components/textbox/index.md",demos:{"87d726e5":{name:"default"},"070e4e3b":{name:"state"},c48c74dd:{name:"disabled"},"890555d8":{name:"disabled-has-state"}}}}}]);